children.strValue: We are sisters who LOVE to travel, try new things, and experience all that life has to offer! We currently live in Los Angeles, but are hoping to be able to travel and live in different parts of the world in the near future.

Hey eveyone! Just wanted to show another interview that we did recently with Tripfilms! We upload our travel videos on this site and they have been really awesome to us over there. Check out Tripfilms for really cool travel videos!
